claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table listing trade names and manufacturers of quadrivalent influenza vaccines (Fluad Quadrivalent, Flublok Quadrivalent, FluMist Quadrivalent), their presentations (e.g., 0.5-mL prefilled syringe or intranasal sprayer), age indications, hemagglutinin antigen content or virus count per dose, administration route, and presence of mercury.
